Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:59.39,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}Chatting without end,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:03.06,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}but there's still so much to say,
