Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:27.97,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I float lightly in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:32.94,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}becoming one with...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:36.77,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}...the distant, glittering sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:39.69,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I read the wind, and wander away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:44.91,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}To a far off destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.41,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Do you want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:50.71,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I fill my lungs and set off,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:54.08,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Taking in the world's spring breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:02:00.34,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}While at the sun above, everyone's smiles are gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:03.30,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}In between our hellos and goodbyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:07.18,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}There is only us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:10.81,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}We can accomplish anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:14.10,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}The rays of the sun pass through,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.94,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Creating a newborn sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:22.70,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}The promised morning arch that we were waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.74,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}As you wave to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:30.54,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}I decide to share with you a special day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:34.12,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}And our idle chatter begins.
