Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break will be over soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then school will start, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we'll see all of our classmates again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:25.67,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, another blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of boys tend to crowd around you. Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I don't think that's even the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anybody a-asked you out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this from Sato-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he liked this kind of thing, and gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual for someone to like candles, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's the candle that he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They showcase a fireworks display every year, if I remember correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of stands with plenty of commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And summer break is going to be over soon, so I'd really like to go with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all wear yukatas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll be nice for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's that then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you guys doing later today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot. I don't want to move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go to karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke is good; I love karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, are you into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can sing most of the popular songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, which ones do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see, that place has really amazing Jambalaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their ramen is unexpectedly good, and their parfaits have large portions of ice cream. {this line seems to be something about Ramen lying in Ambush. Jambalaya is a dish as well as a song, but i totally don't get the other stuff}{she is talking about the food you can order at the karaoke place.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we going to karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a little cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is. I'll order drinks and food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Melon soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grapefruit juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, what do you want to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Iced tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'd like to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like two iced teas, one melon soda, and one grapefruit juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.08,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they have the newest songs from this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.29,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put mine in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...also Jambalaya and potato chips please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.39,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me summer breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.90,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me away, take me summer breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:06.61,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,My love is feeling the breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.91,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me summer breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:13.41,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Gently, touch me summer breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:21.17,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,One summer's dream, taking you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko is really good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really has some talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:29.22,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:35.85,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me summer breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta put another one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru is looking pretty serious over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she stressed out over something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time picking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she staring at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be going next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:15.10,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,A gallant awakening, gravity pulling back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:20.52,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Sneaking out of those days of weeping and cuddling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:26.44,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Best friends fighting off an innocent obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:31.41,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate word is "Love", I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.08,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tell everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:37.08,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,the oracle of our magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:42.67,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mixed up with some trendy words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:46.35,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocha melodical beauty ban ban,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:49.17,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,with a big smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done staring down the song catalogue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it in for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And "send".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your best, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Jambalaya is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hot, so please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The grapefruit juice is for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go, Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The melon soda is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't want to sing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for forcing it on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:26.36,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Touching in the twilight, it's a maiden's naiveté.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:40.83,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,A fruitless love is fine with me, if I could meet you just once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really put some feeling into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two songs to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I sing two more songs, I'll be able to eat eight chips! {literally potatoes}{IN AMERICA WE CALL THEM FRIES}{IN SOVIET RUSSIA, FRIES EAT YOU}{In English we eat fries, not pieces of them. Also, in Britain, where our English comes from, they're chips}{chips come in bags labelled "Lays"}{this group goes by British English and we eat chips}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit worrying and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Tooru, isn't that the song you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never sung before, so I might not be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, it's turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.23,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:56.28,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond the vast hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:10:04.37,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Like 1, 2, 3, there's going to be more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:19.76,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,A white blanket, a puppet with large eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:28.02,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,A polkadot skirt, but we can't share that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:35.73,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we trip, or almost cry, we're still together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:43.08,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the excitement expands, that must be happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:47.08,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:50.87,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,walking straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:59.13,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Like 1, 2, 3, there's going to be more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only three left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't very nice of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody has anything queued up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll put one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that after you're done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for the next song...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next stall over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nobody inside before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they arrive just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a somewhat stifling song.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan, don't sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to sing some karaoke with Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go for another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really enjoyed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I remember seeing a TV show recently about learning how to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I wore a yukata to a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a few of them. Which ones should we wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This colour on this one is stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mature-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I even have one like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is mouldy, and that's why it changed colours...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't wear these just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of my older ones might fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These look grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably belong to Run-chan's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these, I might become as tall as 1*0 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never become an adult like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put them on. How are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers suit you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the festival starts in the evening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only 10 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were a little overexcited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes all of us then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute whatever you wear, Yuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, you've... curled up your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I... do it once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be fireworks for a while, so let's go visit the stands and kill some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go to the mask stand first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, so you're into anime for kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I always get handouts from stands run by the shopping district, so I feel bad. {TLC this}{She is hiding her face so they don't recognize her.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy apple...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, may I have a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, you want some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have some of your cotton candy, Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko and Nagi are tossing rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit number 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, that wins you a set of fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To have fireworks as a prize at a fireworks display...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shooting for the first prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I've already spent this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stands are expensive, so you can't go about wasting your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not be able to buy anything else later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seeing all this stuff sure makes me want to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:17:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be smart and choose things you can enjoy longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shape-cutting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, why don't we do something we can all do together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever played shape-cutting? It's pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go with something easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me finish my yakisoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience; the fireworks display will commence shortly. {there's actually no delay, it's just meaningless japanese politeness, but how do you TL that?}{Thank you for your patience?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks have started already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a nice place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run up there, and we'll be able to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, we're done with shape-cutting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My gourd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right up these stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I care about the fireworks anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, Nagi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us get there in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the finale!{benpatsu da!}{i don't quite get that}{it's "renpatsu"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As of now, the fireworks display is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please take your trash home with you or dispose of it in the proper places.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just seeing the end feels lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I won these fireworks at that stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Nice one, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fret!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A candle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought those?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there nothing but sparklers in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like these somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They {\i1}are{\i0} pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You eat too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, you're here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me another beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you {\i1}are{\i0} alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break was nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also went to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch the fireworks next year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'll complete my shape-cutting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? It was fun, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was unexpectedly immersing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about the end of August, you're thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the sound of cicadas, typhoons...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...summer homework....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Dad, who will finish your handicraft for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...peeing in front of an abandoned house...{=.='''''}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...accidentally get caught while taking photos... {being caught taking photos by mistakes...}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hastily drew the picture diary, but I don't remember what the weather was!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the newspaper that is being recycled before your very eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.85,0:24:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's like this, I still want to see this episode, Bibi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on A Channel, New Term.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we're not in elementary school anymore...
